---
id: research
name: Topic Researcher
description: Generates facts about a topic

input:
  topic:
    type: string
    required: true

output:
  format: json
  schema:
    facts:
      type: array
      description: List of interesting facts about the topic
---
Research the following topic and provide 3-5 interesting facts.

Topic: {{ topic }}

Return JSON with:
- facts: an array of fact strings (3-5 facts)

Focus on lesser-known, interesting information.
